<h2 class="bold font-l">I'll Never Come Back</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After Jason begs for Bruce to kill the Joker for killing him, Bruce redacts by stating that if he does, he'll be going against his code of conduct as a vigilante. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheFettered" class='trope-example-link'>The Fettered</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
