<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="44a98a" data-vimeo-id="406638793" data-video-descrip="After Jason begs for Bruce to kill the Joker for killing him, Bruce redacts by stating that if he does, he'll be going against his code of conduct as a vigilante. " data-video-title="I'll Never Come Back" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/44a98a_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/44a98a.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TheFettered" data-video-tropename="The Fettered" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="11" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/BatmanUnderTheRedHood,ComicBook/Batman,ComicBook/RedHood" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/44a98a.jpg">
